query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_clientes,
  COUNT(DISTINCT clienteHash) as hashes_unicos,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM clientes GROUP BY clienteHash HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) as duplicatas_restantes
FROM clientes;
